data.name: ParagraphStyleCategory
desc: These constants are used to specify the category of paragraph styles in text documents.

items.name: TEXT
lines: is applied to styles that are used for common text.

items.name: CHAPTER
lines: is applied to styles that are used as headings.

items.name: LIST
lines: is applied to styles that used in numberings and lists.

items.name: INDEX
lines: is applied to styles that are used in indexes.

items.name: EXTRA
lines: is applied to styles that are used in special regions like headers, footers, and footnote text.

items.name: HTML
lines: is applied to styles that are used to support HTML.
